// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1872 — Mass File Rename (ransomhouse)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 2f68122b-2eca-5977-9fa9-71310e863e06

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
